---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Patient Treatment Logs & Watchdog Guides | Practical Podiatrist">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-slate-300 relative z-10">
    <header class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-4">Patient Treatment Logs</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">Honest, independent guides to curing complex foot conditions.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/plantar-fasciitis" class="block p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 hover:border-teal-400/40 transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">The 3-Part Plantar Fasciitis Guide</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Master localized fluid clearance, sponge compression mechanics, and the emergency fallback strategy.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/orthotics" class="block p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 hover:border-teal-400/40 transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Exposing the Orthotic Price Trap</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Skip multi-thousand dollar retail store scams and test inserts for torsional stability right in the aisle.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/shoes" class="block p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 hover:border-teal-400/40 transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">The Stability Shoe Matrix</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Vetted breakdowns of Brooks, Hoka, and New Balance models based on structural engineering physics.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
